{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01PRxy6JzFxdNvYRU2VHQczn","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Bug fix (already in working tree, unstaged):** The `handleAPIStepContent` handler had two issues:\n1. It tried to read `step.Config[\"prompt\"]` directly as a file path, but the DSL parser stores the raw `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` string — not just the path. The fix adds `resolveStepConfigFile()` to extract the path from `file(\"...\")` syntax before reading.\n2. It didn't check `step.Config[\"run\"]` for script steps, so clicking a script step with `run = \"...\"` would show \"No content available\". The template also wasn't displaying `run` config keys.\n\n**USAGE.md updates — 3 discrepancies fixed:**\n1. `--image` flag renamed to `--base-image` (matching source code)\n2. Default image changed from `ubuntu:24.04` to `cloche-base:latest` (matching source code)\n3. Added documentation for files created by `cloche init` that were missing: `host.cloche`, `version`, `scripts/prepare-prompt.sh`; also updated the Project Directory Layout section\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":708,"cache_read_input_tokens":89581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":708},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"02bbad21-9ad5-42a1-94f9-f335e96f7c45","uuid":"6d31cce1-5739-4bfc-bc6d-3d6d4a752b8e"}
